race.comment: A qualifier at Caen in June NAFI DE REVE D'OR (5) made the perfect start to her career when debuting with a 1.5L victory at Alencon. Selected to maintain her unbeaten record. NO QUARTER (6) looks a major threat following a 0.75L success when making his debut at Strasbourg. NAXOS DIBAH (3) faded in the closing stages running 14L third at Montier-en-Der on his first outing. Strong claims of breaking his maiden at the second attempt. NEMO DES BROUETS (4) is improving with racing delivering his best effort in three starts to date when 3.5L third at Salon-de-Provence. Of note providing his first start at this venue.
